Name: UCSB
Description: A great University on the California Coast

Name: Murietta Falls
Description: A place near my hometown where I have gone on hikes to. During the spring there is a small waterfall there. A place I find very relaxing. First real big Hike I have ever done and have a lot of fondness towards this place.

Name: Wente Scout Reservation
Description: A summer camp I spent many summers at. Tons of hiking and boating. There was an orienteering course I spent a few summers completing. Just have a lot of fond memories of this place.

Name: Sedona, Arizona
Description: The place where my Grandpa lives. My family spent the last few Christmas's there and it feels like home. It is also a very beautiful place full of beuatiful red rock and great hiking trails.

Name: Zion National Park
Description: My favorite National park. I had a road trip through here a few years ago and want to go back. The most beautiful National park I have been to.

Name: Robertson Park
Description: A place where I had my soccer practices multiple times a week for more than a decade. I found it when I was browsing google maps over my hometown looking for places I have been and had to put it in because of how much time I have spent there and how many memories I have there. There is also a creek that runs north of the fields that is a pleasant place to be.
